03:42.604 --> 03:44.406
Do you think I exploit my workers?

03:44.473 --> 03:46.074
If the shoe fits, wear it.

03:46.075 --> 03:47.742
You know, I say that with love.

03:47.809 --> 03:49.678
Oh, she says that,
if the shoe fits wear,

03:49.744 --> 03:51.113
