04:45.234 --> 04:46.701
I fought at Guadalcanal.

04:46.768 --> 04:48.803
I'm proud to say I've
got a Purple Heart.

04:48.870 --> 04:50.004
You know that reminds me.

04:50.139 --> 04:51.840
My blood work comes back today.

04:51.906 --> 04:54.142
Yeah, you got a Purple
Heart for being wounded

04:54.143 --> 04:55.753
